==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Extrajudicial conveyance
<hw>Extrajudicial conveyance</hw>. <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A conveyance,
as by deed, effected by the act of the parties and not involving, as in
the fine and recovery, judicial proceedings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extralimitary</ent>⟦br⟧
